         <abstract id="aspace_9745cc543157959594f292499e5859aa">The collection includes 84 2 inch square glass lecture slides with content related to the history of psychiatry and a typed list of slides numbered 1-90. Slides include text and images regarding the history of the treatment and housing of people suffering from mental illness in Europe and the United States, including hospitals, restraints and equipment, depictions of mental illness and mental hospitals in art, and historical publications.</abstract>
